Run with: bash chain.sh [ OPTIONS ]
It is prefered to delete your build directory before running.

	  --pull	  pulls the latest docker images from the docker hub. 
          --push	  pushes the to the docker hub of the next argument user id.
	  --debug	  runs in debug mode using valgrind.
-h        --help          displays usages.
-b        --build         builds using the default Dockerfile in current directory.
-f        --force         deletes ignores warnings and removes previous container.
-l        --local         runs without docker container and without ARM compilation
-d        --delete        deletes the toolchain container.
-t	  --transfer	  saves the docker image and sends it to the car over ssh and runs it.
-ba	  --build-arm	  builds using the .armhf Dockerfile in current directory.
